{"tid":824708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄指明日會否繼續停課 言之尚早","createTime":"2018-09-17T07:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:50:45.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7c5e1edbadf620b6e85e3cc97faa0e5d9347f9","tid":824708,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄指明日會否繼續停課 言之尚早<br />\n17/9/2018 14:47<br />\n        教育局局長楊潤雄表示, 當局今早開始跟各間學校聯絡, 知道不同學校, 有不同程度損毀, 政府會按緩急先後, 協助維修校舍, 至於明日會否繼續停課, 楊潤雄就指, 是言之尚早, 要先考慮校舍及交通的具體情況.<br />\n        楊潤雄出席活動後表示, 雖然今日停課, 但各間學校有很多執拾的工作要做, 他感謝校長老師及校工的幫忙, 讓校舍可以盡快開放.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20180917144754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20180917144754&d=XW%2Bx1RxpNmsuaiIKIWoQWfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=331283b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20180917144754</a>"},{"pid":"d00c1fa3f139c2c548ff511dedcb6009fb3a5fc4","tid":824708,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"咁啫係停唔停<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}